### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_AUTH0_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Create Asset (needs Auth0 token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "3D House Model",
  "description": "Beautiful modern house 3D model with high quality textures",
  "price": 29.99,
  "category": "MODELS_3D",
  "previewUrl": "https://example.com/preview.jpg",
  "previewImages": [
    "https://example.com/preview1.jpg",
    "https://example.com/preview2.jpg"
  ],
  "privateFileKey": "assets/private/house-model.blend",
  "fileSize": 5242880
}

### 2. Get All Assets (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets

### 3. Get Assets with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets?category=MODELS_3D&status=ACTIVE&page=1&limit=10

### 4. Search Assets
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets?search=house

### 5. Get Asset by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/1

### 6. Get Assets by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/categories

### 7. Get My Assets (needs Auth0 token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/my-assets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Update Asset (needs Auth0 token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/assets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated 3D House Model",
  "price": 39.99,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 9. Delete Asset (needs Auth0 token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/assets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Increment Download Count (needs Auth0 token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets/1/download
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Categories disponibles:
# MODELS_3D
# CODE_SNIPPETS
# NOTION_TEMPLATES
# GRAPHICS
# VIDEOS
# OTHER

### Status disponibles:
# ACTIVE
# INACTIVE
# PENDING_REVIEW
